VISOR evaluates on three benchmarks for long-horizon visual reasoning: ViDoSeek, SlideVQA, and MMLongBench. These benchmarks are designed to assess the model's performance in visually rich document understanding and question answering tasks. Specifically, ViDoSeek focuses on retrieval-augmented question answering, SlideVQA emphasizes visual question answering on presentation slides, and MMLongBench targets long-context perception across various content types.

